The X Factor - Series 12, Episode 14




Judges' Houses 2

The conclusion of the judges' houses stage, in which the remaining 24 acts set off to glamorous destinations to sing for a place in the competition. They then return to the studio, where - in a new twist to the old format - judges Simon Cowell, Cheryl Fernandez-Versini, Rita Ora and Nick Grimshaw will choose their finalists live in the studio.




Original Air Date: 25-Oct-2015
